Gaussian Naive Bayes based Spam Classifier
________________________________________________
A simple model to classify emails as spam or not spam implemented using only Numpy

Dataset details:
__________________
The dataset consists of 3000 samples in training set and 200 samples in the test set. spambase1.txt contains the description about the attributes used for this problem. 

How to Run
______________________________
Run spamClassifier.py 
Please make sure that the spambasetrain.csv and spambasetest.csv are in the same directory as spamClassifier.py


